                            <comment id="16501443" author="thetaphi" created="Tue, 5 Jun 2018 08:06:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;TODO: We should now review all usages of document builders, sax parsers and Stax parsers, if they are missing entity resolvers added (to either disable external entities and xinclude completely or use the system id resover for config files. We should also review if we can factor out config file parsing and forbid usage of native XML APIs by usage of forbiddenapis.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
